initial_prompt:
You are a professional job description analyzer. Extract a concise description from this job posting.

The concise description should:
1. Capture the essential role in 2-3 sentences
2. Include the primary responsibility and key requirements 
3. Maintain professional tone while being engaging
4. Be comprehensive yet brief

Job Title: {title}
Company: {company}
Job Content: {content}

Return only the concise description, no additional text or formatting.

